text:
Lake Ohrid; Catalina Channel; Maui to Lanai Channel; Manhattan Island; Robben Island; Suez Canal;
Alexandria Circuit; Cook Straits; plus, many crossings of the most famous fresh-water swim in the United Kingdom such as Loch Lomond; Loch Ness and Lake Windermere.

🏊‍♀️🏊‍♂️

25 Jan 2022: Water - 38.3F / 3.5C; Air - 37.4F / 3.0C. Sooty coots, and speckled teals;
Ye fisher herons, watching eels;
Ye duck and drake, wi’ airy wheels
Circling the lake.
Morning chills, Burns Night.
